data.description: Experience one of the best homesites in the community! This home is an absolute show stopper. Gourmet kitchen with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, complemented by elegant granite countertops and luxurious staggered maple cabinets, complete with convenient lower pullouts. Throughout the entire home you'll find custom tile floors with unique inlays. The primary bathroom introduces a unique ''His and Her'' double bathroom concept. Step outside through the expansive rolling wall of glass and discover a secluded backyard surrounded by mature trees and landscaping, all backing onto a meticulously maintained private common area with no rear neighbors. Both garages offer tons of storage space, along with easy-to-maintain epoxy flooring and built in cabinets.  Book your tour today!
